description: Application 1 of 4 for the approval of reserved matters pursuant to conditions 1 and 2 (a-k) attached to outline planning permission dated 22/06/2004 with ref 2001/1894 (as amended) for a mixed use redevelopment of existing timer yard site to provide up to 6390sqm of business (use classes B1 B2 or B8) up to 2710sqm of business units (use class B1 only) 48883sqm of residential floor space (not more than 613 units) 7096sqm of live/work space (not more than 69 units) up to 560sqm of cummunity facilities up to 220sqm of retail space (A1) up to 500sqm of bar/cafe/restaurant space (A3) up to 581 car parking spaces and publicly accessible open space for the general needs/market housing (blocks 4, 9, 19) located on the former Latham's Timber Yard site.
site_number: Altius (Lathams yard & Leeside and Middlesex Wharves)
